---
import Layout from "src/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Experimental Projects">
  <h1 class="mb-2 font-bold text-3xl">Experimental Projects</h1>
  <p>
    These are some of the other projects I have worked on. Most of these
    projects are experiments or prototypes. None the less, I am cool with anyone
    looking at these projects.
  </p>
  <p class="mt-3 text-lg">
    <span class="project_title font-bold">
      Text Editor (C++, QT, CMake, Git)
    </span>
    <br />
    Git Repository: <a
      class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800"
      href="https://github.com/sagedemage/TextEditor"
    >
      TextEditor
    </a>
  </p>
  <ul class="tasks_done list-disc list-inside ml-4">
    <li>Implemented basic file operations</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="mt-3 text-lg">
    <span class="project_title font-bold"> Devoid (C#, MonoGame, Git)</span>
    <br />
    Git Repository: <a
      class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800"
      href="https://github.com/sagedemage/Devoid"
    >
      Devoid
    </a>
  </p>
  <ul class="tasks_done list-disc list-inside ml-4">
    <li>Implemented player and object collision</li>
    <li>Added background music to the game</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="mt-3 text-lg">
    <span class="project_title font-bold">
      Calculator Desktop App (Rust, GTK, Git)
    </span>
    <br />
    Git Repository: <a
      class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800"
      href="https://github.com/sagedemage/CalculatorDesktopApp"
    >
      CalculatorDesktopApp
    </a>
  </p>
  <ul class="tasks_done list-disc list-inside ml-4">
    <li>Implemented basic calculator operations</li>
  </ul>
</Layout>
